138
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:55,320
A woman is not a woman because of reproduction,

139
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,640
but because of her classification against men

140
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,100
that she becomes a female.

141
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:00,680
I think

142
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:03,280
if there were only one sex in this world,

143
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,400
